        All reviews referenced on this site are the result of Net Promoter System (NPS) surveys sent through Delighted® after customers purchased from us.
        NPS scores are on a 0 - 10 scale; we converted them to a 5 star rating by dividing by 2 and then rounding up to the nearest whole number. Any reviews,
        regardless of the rating, that don't have a comment associated with them are not included on this site. For more information about the Net Promoter
