Helix Energy Solutions Group, Inc.

3505 West Sam Houston Parkway North Suite 400
Houston TX 77043 United States
Phone: +1 281-___-____
Fax: +1 281-___-____
http://www.helixesg.com





30
Managers




60
IT employees




$46.8MEST.
IT Budget




Helix Energy Solutions Group is a Houston, TX-based company that runs offshore oil and gas drilling operations while also providing service contracting services to the industry. The company's primary US operations are focused in the Gulf Of Mexico.
Following the departure of the company's CIO, IT is overseen by the Director of Information Technology, who leads the department's day-to-day operations, including responsibility for areas such as information security, and also directs its long-term planning.

The company's infrastructure group focuses… MoreFollowing the departure of the company's CIO, IT is overseen by the Director of Information Technology, who leads the department's day-to-day operations, including responsibility for areas such as information security, and also directs its long-term planning.

The company's infrastructure group focuses on formulation and implementation of the company's network and data storage systems. The unit includes staff that monitor development of the company's server infrastructure.

The applications development unit is in charge of installing Oracle applications for the company's business platforms. The company utilizes the Digital Oil Field suite, an industry-specific set of Oracle products. The company also has teams that handle deployment of ERP applications and HRIS technology.





Sector (Industry)
Energy & Utilities (Oil and Gas)


